fix: definitive fix for auth, buttons, and dashboard

Architecture changes:
- Proxy: stripped to bare clerkMiddleware() with zero custom logic
  to prevent Internal Server Error on edge runtime
- Auth: client-side AuthGuard component using useAuth() hook
  replaces all server-side auth() calls in layouts
- Dashboard: converted to client component that fetches data
  from /api/dashboard endpoint (avoids server component crashes)
- Navbar: replaced Clerk <Show> with useAuth() hook for reliable
  conditional rendering
- Hero: removed motion.div wrappers around links that blocked
  click events, using CSS transitions instead
- All buttons/links across landing page use plain <Link> elements
